Cepta nodded nerviously, still glancing around her. This was all very new to 
her.

"Um, yes please" was her reply to Megatron's question. She wasn't sure who 
these people were, but she guessed that Megatron was her commander, but she 
was still very nervious around all these people.



Antagony looked after Vlad and watched him head for the exit, and then 
looked back at Perndabot. She didn't say anything, waiting for him to speak 
up.
